\">Great Americans series<\/a> <a href=\"http:\/\/en.wikipedia.org\/wiki\/Postage_stamp\" title=\"Postage stamp\">postage stamp<\/a>.<\/p>","name":"Sinclair Lewis","place_of_birth":"Sauk Centre, Minnesota, United States","place_of_death":"Rome, Italy","text":"Sinclair Lewis , Literature, 1930","year":1930.0}